channel.title: RSMV - What music should I use? [Music Chosen, Please Lock]
channel.description:
So I'm going to make a RSMV with my girlfriend.
She's going to be the actor/singer(typer), I'm the editor/choreographer.
I need some advice on what music to use, so that I can tell her and start writing the script.
Preferably a love rock song. NO RAP/COUNTRY
